# Database Setup Instructions:
# 1. Run the SQL script: backend/sql/availability_blocks.sql in your Supabase SQL editor
# 2. This will create the availability_blocks table with proper indexes and constraints
# 3. The table structure:
#    - id: UUID primary key
#    - barber_id: UUID foreign key to barbers table
#    - start_utc: timestamptz for block start time
#    - end_utc: timestamptz for block end time
#    - reason: optional text description
#    - created_at: timestamptz default now()